k8s中多cluster的config配置文件

```
apiVersion: v1
clusters:
- cluster:
    certificate-authority-data: 
    server: https://172.17.4.101:443
  name: ""
- cluster:
    certificate-authority: /Users/apple2/.minikube/ca.crt
    server: https://192.168.99.101:8443
  name: minikube
contexts:
- context:
    cluster: minikube
    user: minikube
  name: minikube
- context:
    cluster: tectonic
    user: tectonic
  name: tectonic
current-context: minikube
kind: Config
preferences: {}
users:
- name: minikube
  user:
    client-certificate: /Users/apple2/.minikube/client.crt
    client-key: /Users/apple2/.minikube/client.key
- name: tectonic
  user:
    client-key-data: 
```
